    foo 1
    bar
  | equals ƒink:
    ·fn
      fn ·ƒret_2:
        ·∅foo fn ·v_5:
          ·let ·v_5, fn ·v_7:
            ·ƒret_2 ·∅bar, 1
      fn ·v_1: ·v_0 ·v_1
    #sourcemaps:ewogICJ2ZXJzaW9uIjogMywKICAic291cmNlcyI6IFsidGVzdCJdLAogICJzb3VyY2VzQ29udGVudCI6IFsiZm9vIDFcbmJhciJdLAogICJtYXBwaW5ncyI6ICJBQUFBLEFBQUE7S0FBQSxPO0lBQUEsQUFBQSxNQUFBLEdBQUEsSTtNQUFBLEFBQUEsS0FBQSxJLEtBQUEsSTtRLEFBQUEsUUFDQSxLLEVBREk7S0FBSixJLEUsQSxLQUFBIgp9


